#################
Requirements
#################
* GCC 4.8+ (compiler)
* Make (build tool)
* libncurses-dev (library dependency)


#################
Build
#################
Unix:
Build by call make.
Clean by call make with target 'clean'.

Windows:
Change to directory win_build.
Update env.bat contents by replacing the existent MinGW binaries path to yours.
Build by execute make.bat.
Clean by execute clean.bat.


#################
Environments
#################
Windows: links standard libraries statically and adds version information to executable
Unix: links standard libraries dynamically